* Verify Deployed\nResources
** Summary Command
***_ databricks bundle summary
** Output
***_ Resource names listed
***_ Direct URLs to workspace
***_ Jobs and pipelines info
** Open in Browser
***_ databricks bundle open <resource>
***_ Opens Databricks UI directly
** Verify
***_ Dev: names have [dev user] prefix
***_ Pipelines in correct state
***_ Schedules paused in dev mode
@endmindmap
